an style="line-height: 115%;">&#4635;&#4821;&#4934;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4661;&#4648;&#4841;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4618;&#4720;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4808;&#4707;</span></span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="line-height: 115%;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4653;</span></span>&#4777;&#4752;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4616;&#4739;&#4901;&#4771;&#4757;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4704;&#4874;&#4828;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4821;&#4899;&#4757;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4808;&#4685;&#4653;&#4707;&#4757;&#4962;</span></span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt"> </span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;" sans-serif="" arial="">[fol.74ra]</span></span><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;</span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4635;&#4741;&#4928;&#4757;&#4725;&#4781;&#4633;&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4635;&#4741;&#4928;&#4757;&#4725;&#4781;&#4633;</span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4961; </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#4770;&#4725;&#4653;&#4661;&#4817;&#4752;</span></span></p><foreign xml:lang="en"><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span arial="" sans-serif="" style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 74: Herewith the book of the epistles of St. John, the Baptist of the Divinity, is completed. And the scribe is F</span>&#601;qur&#228; Iy&#228;sus of Q&#601;fr&#601;ya, of the countries of D&#228;ngw&#228;lo. And the commissioner is G&#228;br&#228; Kr&#601;stos, a son of priest S&#601;m&#705;on of D&#228;br&#228; Ma&#705;&#7693;o. Forgive me and bless us, the sinful, in the time of incense and communion. <span style="line-height: 115%;">[fol.74ra] </span>Your intercession, your intercession do not forget for us!</span></p></foreign>
